Xhops Gold is a welcome return to "good ol' days" of Toppling Goliath but I have to admit I did not love this beer quite as much as some of the reviews I have read. Although it does reclaim some of the characteristics I mentioned above, to me it is only a really good pale ale and not a world class pale ale like TG is known for. 697 charactersmjpolzin, Apr 02, 2016
